Scott: That's why.

901
00:58:21,928 --> 00:58:22,329
Scott: Yeah.

902
00:58:22,950 --> 00:58:27,160
Rym: And FPS is meanwhile, the ones that were well remembered.

903
00:58:27,922 --> 00:58:35,860
Scott: Also battle that was really one of the first ones to run their own server with the, you know, the, uh, and the, um, you know, the Diablo.

904
00:58:36,380 --> 00:58:43,390
Rym: But like FPS is at least like most FPS is if you have the game, the game usually just includes the ability to host a server.

905
00:58:43,731 --> 00:58:46,094
